title: SPACIOUS 2 BED 2 BATH HOME=HWY 16 AND I-405#
posting_body: SPACIOUS 2 BED 2 BATH HOME=HWY 16 AND I-405.with territorial views in the Fairway Drive Condominium complex.
Terrific location is right across the street from the Fairwood Shopping Center and a few blocks from the Fairwood Golf and Country Club.
Complex features a pool, tennis courts and an outdoor brick BBQ.
Easy commuting access to Maple Valley Hwy, Hwy 16 and I-405.
